{"word":"G3592 - ὅδε - hóde - hod'-eh - He","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὅδε</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hóde</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hod'-eh</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">He</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"அது, அந்தி - விளக்கப்பிரதிப் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"this, one here"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>The masculine, feminine (second) and neuter (third) forms. From <a href=\"#/G3588 - ὁ - ho - ho/3588\">G3588</a> and <a href=\"#/G1161 - δέ - dé - deh/1161\">G1161</a>; the <i>same</i>, that is, <i>this</i> or <i>that</i> one (plural <i>these</i> or <i>those</i>); often used as personal pronoun: - he, she, such, these, thus.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}